  ChevronLeft, ChevronRight, Volume2, Bookmark, BookmarkCheck,
  Calendar, Search, X, Moon, Sun, Sparkles, TrendingUp,
  Eye, EyeOff, Menu, BookOpen, AlertCircle, Brain, CheckCircle2,
